<b>Question 1</b>
Consider this logic circuit.
(Image of logic circuit: (NOT A AND B) OR NOT C)

(a) Write a logic expression for this logic circuit. Do not attempt to simplify this logic expression.
X =
(b) Complete the truth table from the given logic circuit.
      </pre>

      <b>Markscheme — Answer (a) (4 marks)</b>
      <pre class="logic">X = (NOT A AND B) OR NOT C</pre>
      <p>(One mark each for: NOT A, AND B, NOT C, OR)</p>

      <b>Markscheme — Answer (b) (4 marks)</b>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <tr><th>A</th><th>B</th><th>C</th><th>X</th></tr>
          <tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr>
          <tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>1</td><td>0</td><td>1</td><td>0</td></tr>
